cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and sentiment classification. The use of deep learning models such as BERT also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves transfer learning, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
